installing metal detectors at
the Temple Mount/Noble Sanctuary

01:51.966 --> 01:54.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
site after an attack on police.

01:54.166 --> 01:59.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
