and Palestinian officials
remained adamant.

02:03.766 --> 02:05.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RAMI HAMDALLAH, Prime Minister,
Palestinian National Authority
(through translator): We

02:05.933 --> 02:09.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
