return to the situation
where things stood before.

02:17.700 --> 02:22.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Palestinians
warned that the new cameras
could see through clothing and

02:22.533 --> 02:25.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
