will not use cameras that
violate anyone's privacy.

02:31.933 --> 02:35.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
An outbreak of cholera
in Yemen was set to reach
400,000 cases today.

02:36.800 --> 02:39.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It has struck a
population already
ravaged by war and hunger.

02:39.033 --> 02:42.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
