are graphic and disturbing.

02:46.666 --> 02:51.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NEIL CONNERY: Tagrid Tatan
barely has the strength to cry.

02:54.400 --> 02:57.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
She's 12 years old.

02:57.833 --> 03:02.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For months, Yemen's children
have paid the highest price in
a war now in its third year.

03:08.233 --> 03:10.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Zara is 15.

03:10.433 --> 03:14.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
