has done to her.

03:14.633 --> 03:19.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And now a cholera epidemic
is spreading, with more
than 5,000 cases every day.

03:21.500 --> 03:26.500 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
