son, Ali, told us.

03:50.500 --> 03:55.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator): My
son died of cholera because the
water is contaminated, and we

03:56.600 --> 03:59.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
