for this well.

03:59.700 --> 04:02.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
We need a solution to
stop this illness that
has killed our children.

04:02.900 --> 04:07.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
NEIL CONNERY: In the
nearby clinic, Tagrid
is finally receiving
help, but, across Yemen,

04:10.733 --> 04:14.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
